data.description: Welcome Home! 205 W Simmons Street is a 3 bed/1 bath home sitting on .69 acres just minutes from Highway 14 and quaint downtown Landrum. This open concept home features a spacious, open living room and kitchen complete with a full appliance package. Down the hall is the primary bedroom as well as two secondary bedrooms that share a hall bath. Outside you will find a covered porch that overlooks the property-including the wooded area behind the backyard. This is the ideal place to relax with your morning cup of coffee or after dinner drink! The backyard offers plenty of space to garden, add a firepit for s’mores, and watch for woodland animals and birds along the back property line! You’ve found your new home for the new year!
